1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 7=

3
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:16,280
Duan Yiran, what are you trying to do?

4
00:00:18,030 --> 00:00:20,120
Why is every man obsessed with you?

5
00:00:20,550 --> 00:00:23,640
I'm taking everything you have.

6
00:00:26,340 --> 00:00:28,580
(Three hours earlier)

7
00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:31,440
Hi.

8
00:00:34,840 --> 00:00:35,750
Why are you here?

9
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:36,790
Where's Qiao Wenjun?

10
00:00:37,670 --> 00:00:38,710
My mom's busy.

11
00:00:38,880 --> 00:00:40,240
So she asked me to come instead.

12
00:00:41,150 --> 00:00:42,240
Then why did you

13
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:43,350
ask me here?

14
00:00:43,750 --> 00:00:47,000
It's about a deeper partnership
between our families.

15
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:50,240
If you invest in Dolphi,

16
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:53,670
both our families
will make a huge profit.

17
00:00:54,710 --> 00:00:56,350
(She clearly has an agenda.)

18
00:00:56,470 --> 00:00:58,920
(Business is probably just an excuse.)

19
00:01:01,710 --> 00:01:02,520
Mr. Song,

20
00:01:05,430 --> 00:01:06,230
what do you think?

21
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:09,310
You're not qualified
to negotiate with me.

22
00:01:10,660 --> 00:01:11,640
Tell Qiao Wenjun to come.

23
00:01:14,710 --> 00:01:18,070
(Fine. How dare you treat me like this?)

24
00:01:18,870 --> 00:01:20,040
(Duan Yiran,)

25
00:01:20,680 --> 00:01:22,040
(you shameful woman.)

26
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:28,070
Get over yourself.
I look down on you too.

27
00:01:28,070 --> 00:01:30,510
What are you doing?

28
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:31,590
You're hurting me!

29
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,950
You promised me.

30
00:01:33,310 --> 00:01:35,840
You said you'd marry me if I behaved.

31
00:01:36,710 --> 00:01:38,510
But now you're seducing another man.

32
00:01:38,870 --> 00:01:41,000
What am I to you? Trash?

33
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,070
Huh?

34
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,790
Oh.

35
00:01:48,790 --> 00:01:52,040
You really think your new status

36
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,710
makes you good enough for me?

37
00:01:56,150 --> 00:01:57,280
Fine.

38
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,950
You.... Fine.

39
00:01:59,710 --> 00:02:00,920
Fine.

40
00:02:01,070 --> 00:02:03,840
Besides, the money my mom gave you

41
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,870
is enough for you to go home
and live easy.

42
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:12,800
Fine.

43
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,240
Hello, Jiang Zechen.

44
00:02:20,750 --> 00:02:21,840
Maple Club.

45
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,120
I have Qiao Wenjun's

46
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:25,310
key evidence for you.

47
00:02:35,750 --> 00:02:36,560
Qiao Nian?

48
00:02:40,310 --> 00:02:41,000
Hello?

49
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:44,400
Well, it's been a long time, Yiran.

50
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:48,360
I know everything you did.

51
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:52,360
Meet me at the abandoned building
by the west warehouse.

52
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:56,590
(What is Qiao Nian planning?)

53
00:02:57,470 --> 00:02:59,840
(Whatever. I'll make sure she dies.)

54
00:03:00,590 --> 00:03:01,400
Hmph!

55
00:03:02,620 --> 00:03:05,020
(Maple Club)

56
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,800
What are you giving me?

57
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:16,470
The footage from Qiao Qibang's fire.

58
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:21,590
How do you have footage from the fire?

59
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:24,190
Ever since I found out

60
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:27,520
Qiao Wenjun and Duan Yiran
were plotting against me,

61
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,800
I prepared ahead of time.

62
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,430
If I remember correctly,

63
00:03:35,310 --> 00:03:37,430
you were the one
who kidnapped Qiao Nian.

64
00:03:37,910 --> 00:03:40,400
I was used by Duan Yiran.

65
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:44,000
Whether you were used or willing,

66
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:47,150
you know the truth better than anyone.

67
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:50,750
Mr. Jiang, you're the only one
who can help me now.

68
00:03:55,470 --> 00:03:56,280
I can't.

69
00:03:58,030 --> 00:03:59,870
You hurt Qiao Nian.

70
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:03,240
I can't trust you.

71
00:04:06,030 --> 00:04:07,560
Before the chairperson's accident,

72
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:10,240
Qiao Wenjun came to see us.

73
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,680
(Audio recording)
See the kidnapping through.

74
00:04:14,910 --> 00:04:18,070
Then pin everything on Bai Niansheng.

75
00:04:19,630 --> 00:04:22,870
You mean I should use marriage
to string him along?

76
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,590
Then trick him into turning himself in?

77
00:04:25,750 --> 00:04:28,160
He keeps trying to earn our favor

78
00:04:28,270 --> 00:04:29,870
so I'll let him marry into the family.

79
00:04:30,870 --> 00:04:32,830
Who does he think he is?

80
00:04:33,510 --> 00:04:37,070
But Mom, do I really have
to marry him after he gets out?

81
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,920
I've already arranged
a backup plan for you.

82
00:04:40,270 --> 00:04:42,510
The Song family's son
is coming back soon.

83
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:45,000
I'll set up a meeting for you two.

84
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:47,480
You'd better not waste this chance.

85
00:04:50,630 --> 00:04:51,480
You want revenge.

86
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,120
Then go straight to Jiang Xiao.

87
00:04:53,950 --> 00:04:55,040
Why come to me?

88
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,360
I've never dealt with Mr. Jiang Xiao.

89
00:04:57,950 --> 00:04:59,190
And I found out

90
00:04:59,190 --> 00:05:01,950
he's closely tied to Qiao Wenjun.

91
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:04,630
For me,

92
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,160
that's not safe.

93
00:05:07,750 --> 00:05:09,360
But I'm Jiang Xiao's son.

94
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,120
But you're the one who cares
about Qiao Nian most.

95
00:05:12,270 --> 00:05:13,600
I've seen it all.

96
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,560
What do you want from me?

97
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:22,870
Protect me.

98
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:24,920
Get me somewhere safer.

99
00:05:26,630 --> 00:05:27,430
Fine.

100
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,040
I promise.

101
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,950
(Qiao Nian, as long as I'm here, )

102
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:40,070
(no one gets to hurt you.)

103
00:05:43,430 --> 00:05:45,310
I'm not the one you
should be angry with.

104
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,390
It's your mom.

105
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,070
How dare you bring up my mom?

106
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,430
If it weren't for you,

107
00:05:51,510 --> 00:05:53,160
my mom wouldn't be so hard on me!

108
00:05:53,310 --> 00:05:54,680
You shameful woman!

109
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,390
This is all your fault!

110
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,430
It's all your fault, you shameful woman!

111
00:06:00,190 --> 00:06:02,240
You shameful woman, it's all your fault!

112
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,160
Stop fooling yourself.

113
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,270
She doesn't love you at all.

114
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:21,870
She's just using you as a tool

115
00:06:21,870 --> 00:06:23,720
to get what she wants.

116
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,310
If she loved you,

117
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:27,510
she wouldn't make you do this!

118
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:29,270
If you fail,

119
00:06:29,270 --> 00:06:30,430
she'll throw you away.

120
00:06:31,270 --> 00:06:32,430
After all these years,

121
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,000
you still can't see it?

122
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:34,830
Shut up!

123
00:06:35,870 --> 00:06:36,720
You shameful woman!

124
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,720
It's your fault!

125
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:46,120
It's your fault for coming back
to the Qiao family.

126
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,680
You stole the love that was mine!

127
00:06:53,630 --> 00:06:54,430
Love?

128
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:57,190
What do you know about love?

129
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:59,000
And you do?

130
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,800
You don't even have a mom.

131
00:07:03,950 --> 00:07:05,720
Didn't you do pretty well on the test?

132
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,510
Mom,

133
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,830
I just wanted to get
into a good college.

134
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,360
Then I could find a good job.

135
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,920
And give you a better life.

136
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,680
Even if you don't get into college,

137
00:07:15,950 --> 00:07:17,390
I'll still take care of you.

138
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:18,950
I got in!

139
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:20,920
Mom!

140
00:07:23,190 --> 00:07:24,830
(Mom doesn't want me anymore.)

141
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,120
Of course I do.

142
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,600
My mom loves me.

143
00:07:33,430 --> 00:07:36,390
She respects me and accepts me
for who I am.

144
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:39,430
She isn't like your mom.

145
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,390
She doesn't treat me like a pawn.

146
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,270
If your mom loved you,

147
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,390
she wouldn't make you do this!

148
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:52,000
Duan Yiran, she's destroying you.

149
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:52,950
You're lying!

150
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:58,160
My mom trusts me.

151
00:07:59,060 --> 00:08:00,720
That's why she trusted me
with this task.

152
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:02,720
What kind of mother

153
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,870
would make her own daughter
hurt someone?

154
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,950
This is all because you won't behave.

155
00:08:07,950 --> 00:08:09,480
You keep going against us.

156
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,750
Duan Yiran,

157
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:16,360
you've fought me since we were kids.

158
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:18,190
But that doesn't change the fact

159
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:21,560
that you two don't have what
it takes to run the company.

160
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,560
Duan Yiran,

161
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,800
you have your own life.

162
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,680
You can break free from her

163
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,630
and live your own life!

164
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,320
You don't get it.

165
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,630
All my life,

166
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,200
no matter what I did,

167
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,510
my mom never approved of me.

168
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,320
That's not your fault.

169
00:08:47,550 --> 00:08:48,870
That's on her!

170
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,840
Once I get rid of you,

171
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:57,790
my mom can secure her place
as CEO of Qiao Group.

172
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,720
That's her lifelong dream.

173
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:04,080
If I help her get what she wants,

174
00:09:05,790 --> 00:09:08,390
I'll prove I'm worth something.

175
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:17,080
Go die.

176
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:22,870
Duan Yiran, what are you doing?

177
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,270
Have you lost your mind?

178
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,720
What are you doing? Are you crazy?

179
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:27,790
Miss.

180
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:34,270
Duan Yiran, what are you doing?

181
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,270
What are you doing?

182
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,390
Duan Yiran!

183
00:10:01,630 --> 00:10:03,240
(I'm actually connected to Jiang Zechen.)

184
00:10:03,870 --> 00:10:05,960
(I actually merged with Jiang Zechen.)

185
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,030
What's going on?

186
00:10:10,630 --> 00:10:12,200
Why do I suddenly feel so hot?

187
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:16,320
And why is my heart racing?

188
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,000
Qiao Nian...

189
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,200
Qiao Nian might be in danger.

190
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:31,480
Qiao Nian...

191
00:10:36,870 --> 00:10:37,670
Hello?

192
00:10:38,550 --> 00:10:39,360
Wen Li,

193
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:40,960
find out where Qiao Nian is.

194
00:10:41,270 --> 00:10:42,080
Okay.

195
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:54,120
Qiao Nian!

196
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,150
Qiao Nian!

197
00:10:56,390 --> 00:10:57,480
Are you okay, Qiao Nian?

198
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,000
I'm getting you out!

199
00:11:05,620 --> 00:11:06,600
Where are you taking...

200
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,790
Stay out of it!

201
00:11:07,790 --> 00:11:09,360
It's dangerous!

202
00:11:09,380 --> 00:11:13,580
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

203
00:11:13,580 --> 00:11:17,060
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

204
00:11:17,060 --> 00:11:21,860
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

205
00:11:21,860 --> 00:11:26,540
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

206
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:34,730
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

207
00:11:35,010 --> 00:11:42,610
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

208
00:11:42,660 --> 00:11:46,450
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

209
00:11:46,970 --> 00:11:50,250
♪Where this ends♪

210
00:11:50,250 --> 00:11:57,530
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

211
00:11:57,530 --> 00:12:01,860
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

212
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:04,980
♪Love turns into pain♪

213
00:12:05,050 --> 00:12:09,170
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

214
00:12:09,330 --> 00:12:12,810
♪Yet I still want you close♪

215
